	<text xml:lang="de">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">[...] ago de rebus novis ad me scriptis, quae et D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8418" cert="high">Myconio</persName> communicavi.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wir haben nüit nüwes, dann juncker <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7537" cert="high">Claus von Hattstet</persName> ist von <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1273" cert="high">Ensesheim</placeName> gon <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augspurg</placeName> gefurt zum keyser; ich acht, er werde um den kopf kürtzer.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="de" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l921" cert="high">Moravia</placeName> ist ein grosse persecution angericht durch <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinandum</persName>; man verjaget vil, verbrent vil; dann der kunig wil die <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20529" cert="high">Waldenser</persName> und <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2589" cert="high">Pikarder</placeName> ußrütten.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die widerteuffer müssen sich ouch liden; dan vil sindt mit einanderen in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l882" cert="high">Ungernn</placeName> zogen, sich dem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Türcken</placeName> ergeben; denen hat ein bassa ein lendlin ingeben zu buwen.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es ist D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p714" cert="high">Cęlio</persName> geschriben, das man das evangelium frey lasse zuͦ <placeName ref="l522" cert="high">Venedig</placeName> predigen on verhinderet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Item zü <placeName ref="l1030" cert="high">Wirtzburg</placeName> prediget man das evangelium; singent psalmen in teutsch.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="manual"><foreign xml:lang="de">Das hat einer gesagt</foreign>, qui suis oculis vidit et audivit.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2916" cert="high">Capitaneus Schertlin</persName> <foreign xml:lang="de">ist zuͦ <placeName ref="l301" cert="high">Leon</placeName></foreign> in domo regni; collegit per suos clam perdites.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Pręsentium literarum latorem, <foreign xml:lang="de">der min schwager ist, den wil ich uch befolhen haben</foreign>, ut illi sis auxilio, si ullam amicitiam cum illis, apud quos hactenus vixit et natus est, habes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Plura brevi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> 20. aprilis 1548.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastius</persName> ex animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reverendo D. domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heynricho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae pastori vigilantissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
